## References & Further Reading

- **Minimal Model:** Bergman RN, Ider YZ, Bowden CR, Cobelli C. "Quantitative estimation of insulin sensitivity." Am. J. Physiol. 1981; 236(6):E667-E677.
- **Codon Optimization:** *Plotkin JB, Kudla G. "Synonymous but not the same: the causes and consequences of codon bias." Nat. Rev. Genet. 2011; 12(1):32-42.*
- **Glucose-Responsive Delivery:** *Zhu L, She H, Meng X, et al. "Enhancement of glucose-responsive insulin secretion from glucose oxidase-modified mesoporous silica nanoparticles." J. Mater. Chem. B. 2013; 1(9):1284-1291.*

